title: Audio lauch date for Bengal Tiger changed
text: Ravi Teja's upcoming film Bengal Tiger is getting ready to hit the screens on November 5. The makers had initially planned to launch the audio on October 17, but now they have now zeroed in on October 18. Bheems Cecireleo is the music director for the film. Directed by Sampath Nandi, the film has Rashi Khanna and Tamannaah as the female leads. Harshvardhan Rane and Bommani Irani are playing crucial roles in the film.
